THE LOCATION:
6 minutes walk to Bronte beach through the trees. 100 steps to the bus stop, corner store and post box. The only sound you'll hear is the birds and wind in the trees. 4 minute walk to famous Italian deli cafe. 8 minute walk through the park to 9 epic Bronte Beach cafes on the water.
